      • Integrated GPS positioning for waste location logging and route optimization<br/>
      • Deployed system on Raspberry Pi for edge computing with Docker containerization<br/>
      <br/>
      <strong>Skills:</strong> ROS, Python, Image Processing, Object Detection, YOLOv8, GPS Integration, Raspberry Pi, OpenCV, Linux, Docker, Git
